Daemos initiated the take off sequence of the Hellgate and flew at full 
speed to the Alliance Island, which was not far from his current location. 
As he arrived, he saw some bots waiting outside of the base.

Daemos:
Well, well. Finally, someone seems happy to see me around. I think I'll 
impress them... Always good for an interview...

As the fighter landed, Daemos got back to his gory beast mode...
